{"data":[{"id":562664927,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"ff719fd583124b627fc5aabd45a3b2f0","url_token":"TAOSHOW","name":"DAVA CHEN","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/53eda59b9a5b0772f0bf35e255992824_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/53eda59b9a5b0772f0bf35e255992824_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/ff719fd583124b627fc5aabd45a3b2f0","user_type":"people","headline":"你想要的，时间会给你答案","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562664927","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546132652,"updated_time":1546133267,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"comment_count":3,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e科学的强大就是：你知道的越多，一些问题看起来就越小儿科。而苦于没有突破，你的回答不会像 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/a1201dc2b83714cd74e1bab6edd827dd\" data-hash=\"a1201dc2b83714cd74e1bab6edd827dd\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$a1201dc2b83714cd74e1bab6edd827dd\"\u003e@王伟\u003c/a\u003e 那样简单的贴一个陈景润的序言，却是开始大肆的嘲讽小儿科。你们不是数学界的清流，是毒瘤！！！！数学的乐趣除了严谨还有天马行空，不过终究还是需要脚踏实地。但这不应该成为别人对于天马行空的否定。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实一直有一个陈氏定律，任何大于0的两个自然数，都能通过简单运算（加减乘除）最后结果是1，eg：1和5，例证：5-（5-1）=1。 我感觉数学史上也可以给我留下一个章节。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我一个三流学校专科生，说真的，真的感觉有的喷的太厉害了。嘴下积德，你可以验证下我的猜想-,-\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个猜想时小学5年级的时候想的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e还记得那个夏天，我考上了我们县的奥赛班，镇上排名第八，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那一年夏天的西瓜真好吃，那一年的农活真的不累\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那一年的赞许真的好听，直到现在我都感觉那是我在学习的海洋里最高的成就，所以自作聪明得到了陈氏定律，此定律时在干农活（我们县城以柳编出名）扒条子（土话)的时候想到的，从小学到初中，从初中到高中，虽然成绩已经不堪回首，但这个定律却一直没有忘记，可能当成了一个笑话，但是我相信，数学者，或者学家一定能通过验证，得到这个条件成立的公式数最低是几，就像陈老的1+2，终究会证明出三个运算值还是五个运算值。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e此定律因为是一半，所以特许学者进行验证，可以署名如：陈庞定律。陈许定律，陈牛定律，陈陈定律。等等吧。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"科学的强大就是：你知道的越多，一些问题看起来就越小儿科。而苦于没有突破，你的回答不会像 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/a1201dc2b83714cd74e1bab6edd827dd\" data-hash=\"a1201dc2b83714cd74e1bab6edd827dd\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$a1201dc2b83714cd74e1bab6edd827dd\"\u003e@王伟\u003c/a\u003e 那样简单的贴一个陈景润的序言，却是开始大肆的嘲讽小儿科。你们不是数学界的清流，是毒瘤！！！！数学的乐趣除了严谨还有天马行空，不过终究还是需要脚踏…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.au